QuestData.Title: Ghouls Hate My Grains
QuestData.Description: You're a pro at this, $n! A regular junior botanist! Listen, I've got a new seed to try called the rocknut. Use it to block the undead. Just drop it down and they'll stop dead in their tracks. Undead are so stupid!$B$BLet's give it a try!
QuestData.RewardText: I think that made Stillwater angry. He's sending the heavy-hitters after us now. No time to lose, friend, let's go!
